he Lerp Legend. It's a mash of my backpack. Right next to the match in my backpack. It's a definite mess in my backpack. As well as my life. Fuck the hype. My back has no scars at all. That shit's hella clean. Cause I'm the one holding the knife. It feels nice to be a Lerp Legend. I could be a Lerp Lesson. For you or anyone in your crew. Anyone of you. I'm the Lerp Legend. Lerp Legend. Lerp Legend. Lerp Legend. I'm the Lerp Legend. Lerp Legend. Lerp Legend. Lerp Legend. I swear man I didn't take that. It wasn't me man. I swear to God bro. Come on let me do it. Stop it bro. I finally did it. I told you man. I'm not the Lerp Legend.",
